title: TiddlyPWA
tags: [[TiddlyPWA Docs]]


Have you ever wanted to combine the power and customizability of [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com]] and
the convenience of a modern offline-friendly, encrypted, synced notes app? Now you can! With…

<div class="tpwadoc-logos" role="presentation">
	{{$:/plugins/valpackett/tiddlypwa/icon}}
	{{$:/biglogo.svg}}
</div>

TiddlyPWA turns TiddlyWiki5 into an ''offline-first'' [[Progressive Web App|https://web.dev/learn/pwa/progressive-web-apps/]]
with ''encrypted'' local persistent storage and efficient ''synchronization'' with a server that can easily be hosted for free.

